nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROB base ; Drug X; one compartment ; estimat $INPUT ID TIME AMT DROP DV MDV $DATA ../../../data/dat1.csv ignore=@
$SUBR ADVAN1 TRANS2 $EST MET=1 PRINT=5 NOABORT INTER
$PK TVCL = THETA(1) TVV = THETA(2)
CL = TVCL * EXP(ETA(1)) V = TVV * EXP(ETA(2))
S1 = V
$ERROR
IPRED = F Y = IPRED * (1 + ERR(1))
$THETA (0, 5) ; CL (0, 20) ; V
$OMEGA 0.1 0.1
$SIGMA 0.01 $COVR $TAB ID TIME AMT DV MDV IPRED PRED CWRES NPDE NOPRINT NOAPPEND ONEHEADER FILE=r2.tab $TAB ID CL V ETAS(1:LAST) NOPRINT NOAPPEND FIRSTONLY ONEHEADER FILE=r2par.tab
